Configuring build environment

Ubuntu 12.04

1) apt-get install:
  make
  xsltproc
  docbook-xml docbook-xsl docbook-xsl-doc-html
  subversion

2) get fop (/home/petya/petya-old/petya/fop/trunk-2010-04-20/fop):

http://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/

3) get current version of Oracle (Sun) Java - 6/7/8 (?)

4) CPAN modules (for tools):
  Yandex::Tools
